snippet.title: Jets'n'Guns 2 official trailer
snippet.description:
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/830820/JetsnGuns_2/ 
Jets'n'Guns 2 is a classic side-scrolling shooter of unlimited action and destruction!

As an elite space pilot jump into an epic adventure to save the universe from inevitable doom. Travel the galaxies and unleash an arsenal of the deadliest weapons and devices ever installed in a spaceship!

Visit our channels to get more info!
Rake in Grass homepage: http://www.rakeingrass.com
FaceBook: http://www.facebook.com/rakeingrass

Twitter: https://twitter.com/rakeingrass
